parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light blinks or remains illuminated
the airbag system malfunctions
the airbags fail to deploy in the event of a crash
the passenger side airbag control module needs to be replaced.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unexpected deployment of the airbag can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The airbag explodes without warning
knocking the driver unconscious
and causing the vehicle to lose control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause loss of steering control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks up
the vehicle makes a clunking noise when turning
the steering column pops and jolts slightly when turning
power steering loss
and the vehicle is difficult to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loud squealing and grinding noise from the brakes can cause distraction and loss of control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The brakes make a loud squealing and grinding noise
even when the pads and rotors are fine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle's instability and swerving can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle swerves excessively on the freeway
making it difficult to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Sudden loss of brake function
loud squealing or grinding noise when applying the brakes
vibration or instability when braking
brake pedal sticking to the floor
inability to stop the vehicle
loud scraping noise from the passenger side front.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The noise and vibration caused by the brake system can be a precursor to brake failure, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Loud squealing or grinding noise when applying the brakes
vibration or instability when braking
loud scraping noise from the passenger side front.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sticking of the brake pedal can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal sticking to the floor
inability to stop the vehicle
loud scraping noise from the passenger side front.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) can cause the vehicle to lose stopping power, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall, shut off unexpectedly, and experience issues with door locks, leading to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while in motion or stationary
doors lock/unlock inconsistently
batteries drain quickly
and warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock system can cause inconvenience and safety risks, especially if the doors become stuck or unable to unlock.
symptoms: Doors do not unlock with the power locks
doors lock/unlock inconsistently
and manual intervention is required to open the doors.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbags do not deploy in the event of an accident
